Cheese Tortellini
via https://culinaryginger.com/cheese-tortellini/

Dough: see pasta recipe from good eats

Filling:

8 ounces (250 grams) fresh ricotta
1 extra large egg
1/2 cup (45 grams) Parmesan cheese, freshly grated
2 tablespoons fresh spinach, chopped
1/2 teaspoon dried basil
1/8 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper
Small pinch of nutmeg, freshly grated
1 egg, beaten with 1 teaspoon water for egg wash


Add all the ingredients to a mixing bowl and mix until well incorporated. Set aside.

Assembly: see this video https://youtu.be/2QPcSCsWpXw?t=27

